  "texts": [
    "We adopt the implementation in the nanoflann project [57].",
    "❺ ANN: a kd-tree-based library [3] providing both exact and approximate kNN search.",
    "If a non-negative error parameter is provided, ANN ensures the retrieved i-th nearest neighbor is a (1 +)-approximation to the true i-th nearest neighbor by using the priority search algorithm [6].",
    "In our benchmark, we tune in range [0, 5] to control the trade-off between query efficiency and result accuracy.",
    "❻ octree: the generalized octree index that can be regarded as an adaptive and recursive grid index."
  ],
